{"article_id":"bgnXjskKXhs4ZzwV","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Senator Mitt Romney is pursued by reporters","depth":4},{"id":1,"text":"as he arrives for the fourth day of the Senate impeachment trial of President Donald Trump in Washington , January 24 , 2020 .","depth":4},{"id":2,"text":"( Erin Scott/Reuters )","depth":3},{"id":3,"text":"Senator Mitt Romney","depth":8},{"id":4,"text":"( R. , Utah )","depth":8},{"id":5,"text":"said on Monday","depth":7},{"id":6,"text":"that it looks \" increasingly likely \"","depth":7},{"id":7,"text":"there will be enough Republican votes","depth":8},{"id":8,"text":"to call former White House national security adviser John Bolton to testify in the Senate impeachment trial .","depth":8},{"id":9,"text":"\" I think","depth":8},{"id":10,"text":"it ' s increasingly likely that other Republicans will join those of us","depth":9},{"id":11,"text":"who think","depth":10},{"id":12,"text":"we should hear from John Bolton , \"","depth":10},{"id":13,"text":"Romney told reporters .","depth":7},{"id":14,"text":"\" I have spoken with others","depth":7},{"id":15,"text":"who have opined upon this . \"","depth":7},{"id":16,"text":"Romney did not indicate which Senators","depth":6},{"id":17,"text":"he believed","depth":7},{"id":18,"text":"would vote in favor of Bolton ' s testimony .","depth":7},{"id":19,"text":"Senator Susan Collins","depth":8},{"id":20,"text":"( R. , Maine )","depth":8},{"id":21,"text":"said in early January","depth":7},{"id":22,"text":"that she was working with \" a fairly small group \" of GOP Senators","depth":7},{"id":23,"text":"to allow witnesses at the trial .","depth":7},{"id":24,"text":"Romney ' s comments came","depth":6},{"id":25,"text":"after a New York Times report on Sunday alleged","depth":7},{"id":26,"text":"that Bolton wrote in his upcoming book","depth":8},{"id":27,"text":"that President Trump told the former adviser","depth":9},{"id":28,"text":"he had conditioned military aid to Ukraine on that country ' s commitment","depth":10},{"id":29,"text":"to investigate corruption allegations against Joe and Hunter Biden .","depth":10},{"id":30,"text":"On Monday morning Republican Senators canceled a scheduled press briefing .","depth":5},{"id":31,"text":"President Trump has repeatedly denied","depth":6},{"id":32,"text":"demanding an investigation into the Bidens in exchange for the release of military aid .","depth":6},{"id":33,"text":"Trump also denied Bolton ' s reported allegation on Sunday evening .","depth":6},{"id":34,"text":"\" I NEVER told John Bolton","depth":10},{"id":35,"text":"that the aid to Ukraine was tied to investigations into Democrats ,","depth":11},{"id":36,"text":"including the Bidens .","depth":11},{"id":37,"text":"In fact , he never complained about this at the time of his very public termination , \"","depth":9},{"id":38,"text":"the President wrote on Twitter .","depth":8},{"id":39,"text":"\" If John Bolton said this ,","depth":8},{"id":40,"text":"it was only to sell a book . \"","depth":8},{"id":41,"text":"As late as last Friday , GOP Senate aides had said","depth":3},{"id":42,"text":"Democrats would probably not be able to get the votes","depth":4},{"id":43,"text":"needed to summon witnesses","depth":5},{"id":44,"text":"to give testimony .","depth":5},{"id":45,"text":"Republicans currently hold a 53-47 majority ,","depth":3},{"id":46,"text":"so Democrats will need to convince four Republican Senators to gain enough votes","depth":4},{"id":47,"text":"to summon witnesses .","depth":4}],"relations":[{"parent":95,"left":88,"right":94,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":88,"left":50,"right":87,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":50,"left":49,"right":2,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":49,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":87,"left":70,"right":86,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":70,"left":62,"right":69,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":62,"left":55,